16 WHEREAS, this year, the International WeLoveU Foundation celebrates 20 years of
17 conducting blood drives through Chairwoman Zahng Gil-jah's commitment to public service
18 and humanitarian efforts, inspiring citizens to embody love for humanity and promote world
19 peace.
20 NOW, THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED BY THE HOUSE OF REPRESENTATIVES that
21 the members of this body recognize and commend the International WeLoveU Foundation
22 for its many outstanding contributions on behalf of those in need as well as extend best
23 wishes for continued success.
24 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that the Clerk of the House of Representatives is authorized
25 and directed to make an appropriate copy of this resolution available for distribution to the
26 International WeLoveU Foundation.
